WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:08.720
Well, I'm doing this prayer video live because I was going to make a video already today for tomorrow.

00:00:08.720 --> 00:00:22.594
But after I got all the emails for the earthquake that just took place off the coast of Russia, I felt led to pray over people's protection because of the tsunami warnings that they're having.

00:00:22.594 --> 00:00:40.587
And so, I want everybody to come together, and we're just going to take authority and pray over the coastlines of Hawaii, Japan, the West Coast of the United States of America, and parts of Alaska because, you know, we have power and authority over all this stuff, folks.

00:00:40.587 --> 00:00:45.246
And so, we'll put our angels out there watching over these people.

00:00:45.246 --> 00:00:49.840
We're the salt and we're the light, and that's what our job is.

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:56.709
And when God gives us these harbingers, these warnings through prayer telling us that they were coming...

00:00:56.709 --> 00:00:57.486
How many weeks ago?

00:00:57.486 --> 00:00:59.309
He said, "A major one is about to take place.

00:00:59.309 --> 00:01:01.964
" And it did, just like the Lord told us.

00:01:02.346 --> 00:01:12.199
But it's not the one—I've seen that one up there, and then I see the one on the Oregon coastline, and it will be very devastating from what I have seen.

00:01:12.579 --> 00:01:18.680
So, we take authority and pray over the people of Oregon and over Washington because it's the Ring of Fire.

00:01:18.680 --> 00:01:26.920
And this is the pressure that I warned you all about that's coming, a shaking in the atmosphere, a shaking in the soil.

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:32.284
And the Lord told me, He said, "Great pressure will come on the soil in the days ahead.

00:01:32.284 --> 00:01:38.010
" And then there's other articles that are being sent to us about the asteroids saying, "Hey, it's going to hit the moon.

00:01:38.010 --> 00:01:43.280
" Now, I thought that was kind of interesting because of what the Lord was telling me about the tides.

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:45.680
He said, "The tides will change.

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:48.133
There'll be unusual tides.

00:01:48.133 --> 00:01:51.010
They'll come further in than ever before.

00:01:51.010 --> 00:01:54.720
" And He said, "And they'll go out further than they ever have before.

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:57.239
" He said, "Watch the tides," if you all remember.

00:01:57.239 --> 00:02:01.280
And so, these are the things that I've been praying over.

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:05.988
And over Italy—unusual tides in Italy, over...

00:02:06.422 --> 00:02:07.726
was it Venice?

00:02:07.726 --> 00:02:09.550
Yeah, that's what the Lord was talking to me about.

00:02:09.550 --> 00:02:13.234
And so, those are the things that I've been praying over.

00:02:13.234 --> 00:02:17.218
But I can tell you what's happened in the last couple of days with me.

00:02:17.218 --> 00:02:20.669
But maybe we'll just go straight into prayer today on this video.

00:02:20.979 --> 00:02:26.000
I was going to talk about some things the Lord had for you; I guess I can go over that.

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:44.114
He was talking about being obedient and listening to his still small voice, and that it wouldn't have to be, you know, like with body language and how you can sense whenever your spouse is upset about something.

00:02:44.114 --> 00:02:45.760
They don't have to use words.

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:56.366
But following the voice of God so strong, following that inward peace, so that He doesn't have to speak when you're mature and you've been around somebody a long time.

00:02:56.366 --> 00:02:58.080
They don't have to say something.

00:02:58.080 --> 00:03:01.1000
A lot of times, you already know what they're feeling just by how they're acting, right?

00:03:01.1000 --> 00:03:11.943
And your wife, you know, you're sitting next to your wife in the car or something, and you know if there's something bothering her or not just because of her mannerisms, right?

00:03:11.943 --> 00:03:18.320
And so, that was what the Lord was talking to me about—listening to the mannerisms, listening to Him.

00:03:18.320 --> 00:03:20.119
He doesn't have to...

00:03:20.119 --> 00:03:24.293
If He's not saying something, follow that peace that passes all understanding.

00:03:24.293 --> 00:03:25.840
There's many of you...

00:03:26.834 --> 00:03:30.240
There's so much confusion, and that's why I see the emails.

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:35.177
My wife tells me, she says, "Brandon, people are thinking they're hearing the Lord, Brandon, and they're not.

00:03:35.508 --> 00:03:35.840
They're not.

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:39.817
There are familiar spirits that are messing with these people.

00:03:39.817 --> 00:03:52.319
" And that's why I made the video today going back to the ABCs of Christianity: reading your Bible, praying, going to church, volunteering, doing the things that you've got to do.

00:03:52.319 --> 00:03:55.657
Do the ABCs, but don't just go around hearing voices.

00:03:55.657 --> 00:03:56.959
That's what I was talking about.

00:03:56.959 --> 00:03:58.333
There's a lot of people just hearing voices.

00:03:58.333 --> 00:04:04.460
They're, you know, "I hear this voice and I followed it and I did this," and I'm thinking, "Well, don't do that.

00:04:04.460 --> 00:04:10.788
" You've got to test the spirits and you've got to pray in the spirit, or pray in English, whatever you know how to do.

00:04:10.788 --> 00:04:11.794
Pray, worship, get into worship.

00:04:13.049 --> 00:04:16.791
And I have this for you: I was hurting really bad in my hip.

00:04:16.791 --> 00:04:23.751
I hadn't made a video because I don't know what I did, but it was so bad I couldn't even get out of my chair.

00:04:23.751 --> 00:04:28.453
I was under attack, and it was hurting so bad I couldn't move.

00:04:28.453 --> 00:04:31.500
And so, I laid down and I couldn't even turn over in bed.

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:37.440
It was the most excruciating pain I've ever had.

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:43.759
And I told my wife, I said, "I might have to have you take me to the hospital because that's how bad this is.

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:46.320
" And all of a sudden, I started praying.

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:47.714
And I was praying and praying and praying and praying.

00:04:48.103 --> 00:04:50.251
I said, "Lord, I thank you that I'm healed," and all this stuff.

00:04:50.251 --> 00:04:55.590
He said, "Stop praying and start worshiping.

00:04:56.046 --> 00:04:57.383
Start worshiping me.

00:04:57.383 --> 00:05:04.660
" So, I just started singing songs, started worshiping the Father in here, and the glory of the Lord started to come.

00:05:04.660 --> 00:05:05.699
I could feel it.

00:05:05.699 --> 00:05:08.650
And in His presence, there's fullness of joy; there's fullness of peace.

00:05:08.650 --> 00:05:13.440
And I was still feeling that pain, and He said, "Move your leg.

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:15.439
" I said, "Move my leg?

00:05:15.439 --> 00:05:16.639
I'm in pain!

00:05:16.639 --> 00:05:18.720
I don't want to move my leg.

00:05:34.220 --> 00:05:39.415
" He said, "Move your leg.

00:05:39.415 --> 00:05:44.253
" Okay, so I moved my leg, and I lifted my leg.

00:05:45.474 --> 00:05:50.720
And all of a sudden, out of that little bit of obedience, the pain subsided a little bit.

00:05:50.720 --> 00:05:52.023
He said, "Sing.

00:05:52.023 --> 00:05:54.640
" So, I started singing, and I moved my leg.

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:10.079
He said, "Stop moving your leg.

00:06:10.079 --> 00:06:11.813
Tell Diana to sing.

00:06:20.524 --> 00:06:20.836
" So, she started singing, started worshiping, and all of a sudden, that pain level went down a little bit more.

00:06:20.836 --> 00:06:24.299
I said, "Well, my goodness, this is amazing.

00:06:24.299 --> 00:06:30.865
" Because I'm telling you, it was on a scale of one to 10, it was a 20.

00:06:30.865 --> 00:06:37.417
That's how bad this pain was.

00:06:38.174 --> 00:06:39.760
It was awful, and I was crying out.

00:06:41.419 --> 00:06:42.179
I said, "I need mercy right now.

00:06:55.394 --> 00:06:55.691
" He said, "Sing.

00:06:58.479 --> 00:06:58.709
" So, I started singing more.

00:07:04.769 --> 00:07:05.059
He said, "Lift your leg.

00:07:06.220 --> 00:07:08.720
" So, I lifted my leg and I moved my leg.

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:14.960
He said...

00:07:24.132 --> 00:07:24.319
It's just the still small voice.

00:07:24.999 --> 00:07:29.260
It's the obedience of the little thing, even if it sounds foolish.

00:07:29.260 --> 00:07:30.000
Listen.

00:07:43.072 --> 00:07:43.208
He said, "Turn your body over, get on the floor, and move yourself where you can stand on one foot and hop.

00:07:52.380 --> 00:07:52.680
" I said, "Lord, I'm in excruciating pain.

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:55.240
" But I said, "Lord, I'll do it.

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:05.280
" So, I turned over out of the side of my bed and I started bouncing on the foot that didn't hurt, and the pain started lifting even more.

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:07.200
I said, "Well, that was really interesting.

00:08:07.200 --> 00:08:12.720
" And now, I was able to move a little bit so I could go to the restroom.

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:16.373
So, He said, "Go to the restroom.

00:08:16.373 --> 00:08:26.669
" So, I hobbled into the restroom, and by the time I got there, the pain lifted a little bit more.

00:08:44.399 --> 00:08:44.799
And then He said, "Now, sing more.

00:08:44.799 --> 00:08:49.490
" So, I started singing more and I started worshiping the Father.

00:08:49.490 --> 00:08:50.649
"Thank you, Father.

00:08:50.649 --> 00:08:51.519
Thank you.

00:08:58.169 --> 00:08:58.760
" I made it to the hall, and He said, "Walk quickly.

00:09:08.067 --> 00:09:08.320
" I said, "Walk?

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:11.840
I can barely.

00:09:11.840 --> 00:09:21.920
" So, I hobbled, starting to move down the hall, and the pain lifted a little bit more.

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:24.548
And I told her, "It's lifting.

00:09:35.510 --> 00:09:35.760
" But it's as I take every single step of obedience in what He's asking me to do, even if it's not something that my flesh wants to do.

00:09:35.760 --> 00:09:44.740
I'm following the voice of God and what He's instructed me, even if it doesn't make sense.

00:09:44.740 --> 00:09:50.860
So, I get down all the way, and He said, "Now, go sit on the side of your bed again.

00:09:50.860 --> 00:09:57.741
" So, all these little steps of pain that was so intense that I couldn't move...

00:09:57.741 --> 00:10:01.060
and I kept listening, I kept listening, I kept listening.

00:10:14.697 --> 00:10:15.120
And by the time it was like 1:00, whatever it was, it was terrible.

00:10:15.120 --> 00:10:16.940
Boom, it just started lifting completely.

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:21.326
And He said, "Go to sleep.

00:10:21.326 --> 00:10:22.560
" So, I went to sleep.

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:26.360
When I woke up, it was completely gone.

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:40.373
But what I'm trying to tell you is in the word that He gave me within that 24 hours, He said, "This is what it's going to take to walk in the greater glory.

00:10:47.707 --> 00:10:47.991
" Even if it doesn't make sense what I'm instructing you to do, you just obey me even if it's painful.

00:10:47.991 --> 00:10:49.240
Do you understand?

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:59.240
Following the voice of God beyond your intellect in these last days, even if it doesn't make sense to your natural mind.

00:11:02.960 --> 00:11:03.988
The natural man perceiveth not the things of the Lord.

00:11:21.291 --> 00:11:21.794
And in these last days, for what's about to take place, you must obey Him at all costs, even if it doesn't make sense.

00:11:21.794 --> 00:11:23.680
"Jump on one leg.

00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:24.747
" "I'm in pain.

00:11:24.747 --> 00:11:25.680
" "Jump on one leg.

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:26.229
" Boing, boing, boing.

00:11:27.462 --> 00:11:27.668
It lifts.

00:11:35.248 --> 00:11:35.456
I go, "Well, I'll be.

00:11:36.288 --> 00:11:39.780
" And that's what He was talking to me about—obeying Him at all costs.

00:11:46.100 --> 00:11:46.350
And He gave me an illustration because I watched Billy Burke.

00:11:46.350 --> 00:11:54.959
He'll be ministering to somebody, and all of a sudden, he will get a word of knowledge for another person instantaneously.

00:11:54.959 --> 00:12:06.040
He'll turn and minister that word of knowledge that he's getting from the Father instantaneously to that other person.

00:12:11.968 --> 00:12:13.120
The other person's there, and it's awkward, and they'll be looking at him like you're rude.

00:12:13.120 --> 00:12:18.826
But he'll follow the voice of God at all costs, and the anointing follows.

00:12:18.826 --> 00:12:20.106
It flows.

00:12:20.106 --> 00:12:25.940
It's not what you think you should be doing at that moment.

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:29.680
And the Lord showed me.

00:12:32.036 --> 00:12:35.152
He said, "It's not what you think you should be doing at the moment.

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:42.520
It's following My voice, even if it doesn't make sense.

00:12:49.360 --> 00:12:52.789
" And what we're going to come to in the days ahead, going into the fall, going into this new season, He said an acceleration of things is about to take place.

00:13:05.706 --> 00:13:06.053
You're about to see things change like you've never seen them change before.

00:13:06.053 --> 00:13:13.497
And if you want to flow with Me, you're going to have to obey Me when it doesn't make sense.

00:13:27.006 --> 00:13:27.337
And that's what He's been instructing me about.

00:13:41.759 --> 00:13:51.235
I was invited to do certain things, and it looked all beautiful, but the Lord said, "This is not peace.

00:13:51.235 --> 00:13:55.165
I'm not giving you a go on this.

00:13:55.165 --> 00:13:58.159
" Well, I don't understand, Father.

00:13:58.159 --> 00:14:00.410
Isn't this the door?

00:14:00.410 --> 00:14:05.119
Isn't this what You want me to do?

00:14:05.119 --> 00:14:06.930
He said, "No, don't do this.

00:14:10.986 --> 00:14:16.560
" And it's uncomfortable for your flesh, but follow what I tell you to do, even if it doesn't make sense to you.

00:14:21.379 --> 00:14:21.609
"But I'm going to show you some things concerning this.

00:14:25.940 --> 00:14:26.250
" So, He gave me a download.

00:14:30.587 --> 00:14:35.736
It was a word of correction for some things.

00:14:35.736 --> 00:14:39.360
And it was so clear what the Holy Spirit was showing me.

00:14:40.470 --> 00:14:41.580
But the enemy came immediately.

00:14:42.900 --> 00:14:45.576
He's like, "Oh, you're not hearing the voice of God.

00:14:45.576 --> 00:14:47.451
" It was torment.

00:14:47.451 --> 00:14:55.760
Fear has torment, but perfect love casteth out all fear.

00:14:55.760 --> 00:15:17.920
So, I'm dealing with the balance of your flesh and the spirit, because your flesh wants money, because you want the provision, you want all this stuff, and you're trying to get it, and you think, "Oh, there's money involved.

00:15:30.720 --> 00:15:31.040
This is a blessing.

00:15:36.832 --> 00:15:37.088
" And the Lord said, "Reject that.

00:15:37.088 --> 00:15:38.062
Don't take that.

00:15:38.062 --> 00:15:40.107
Do what I tell you to do.

00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:46.456
" And it's listening to Him at all costs, even if it doesn't make sense to your flesh.

00:15:46.456 --> 00:15:49.911
Because this individual said, "Hey, we want to bless your ministry," and it's a lot.

00:15:55.264 --> 00:15:55.408
I was like, "Oh my goodness, praise God.

00:15:55.408 --> 00:15:59.813
" But the Lord said, "No, will you listen to Me even when it doesn't make sense?

00:15:59.813 --> 00:16:00.853
" Yes, Lord.

00:16:00.853 --> 00:16:01.973
Yes, Lord.

00:16:01.973 --> 00:16:04.026
So, I follow the voice of God.

00:16:07.360 --> 00:16:08.200
This is what He tells me to do, and this is what I'm trying to tell you to do.

00:16:08.200 --> 00:16:09.977
Go back to the basics.

00:16:09.977 --> 00:16:13.012
Go back to your first love.

00:16:13.012 --> 00:16:22.520
He started talking to me about the book by John Bevere, "The Awe of God".

00:16:27.680 --> 00:16:27.850
And He said there must be a reverent fear.

00:16:27.850 --> 00:16:29.383
Not like, "Oh, I'm scared of God.

00:16:42.840 --> 00:16:43.200
" I'm talking about reverencing Him and being in awe of Him because of who He is.

00:16:56.160 --> 00:16:56.787
He is a God that is to be feared.

00:17:02.772 --> 00:17:03.146
And we're not giving Him enough reverence in these days.

00:17:03.146 --> 00:17:14.026
It's the still, small voice, but obeying the still, small voice even whenever it doesn't make sense, and fear Him.

00:17:14.026 --> 00:17:22.119
This is what He says to do, and it's not what your intellect thinks you should be doing.

00:17:22.119 --> 00:17:25.760
It's following Him at all costs.

00:17:25.760 --> 00:17:27.839
Awe of God.

00:17:29.580 --> 00:17:32.711
And He said, "Go back, and you need to read the book again.

00:17:32.711 --> 00:17:38.693
Read the first several chapters of John Bevere's book again.

00:17:38.693 --> 00:17:39.510
You're missing it.

00:17:42.719 --> 00:17:48.639
You need to go back to the basics of what I've told you.

00:17:48.639 --> 00:17:51.650
Don't deviate just because all this stuff's coming at you.

00:17:51.650 --> 00:17:55.839
" "Hey, we have a conference for you over here.

00:17:55.839 --> 00:18:00.658
We have a conference for you over here.

00:18:00.658 --> 00:18:02.551
" "What have I told you to do?

00:18:02.551 --> 00:18:07.956
Raise up prayer warriors for this time, in these end times.

00:18:07.956 --> 00:18:10.914
Bring a million-man and woman prayer army.

00:18:15.039 --> 00:18:15.290
That's your assignment.

00:18:15.290 --> 00:18:16.548
Don't deviate from it.

00:18:23.253 --> 00:18:23.600
" Do you understand?

00:18:29.039 --> 00:18:30.862
And the shiny thing is really shiny, and it can distract you.

00:18:30.862 --> 00:18:32.867
What did God say?

00:18:35.600 --> 00:18:39.850
And that's what I want you to go back to in your life today, ladies and gentlemen.

00:18:39.850 --> 00:18:41.1000
Go back to, what did God say?

00:18:41.1000 --> 00:18:46.989
Do you have an inward peace to do for the Father on a day-to-day basis?

00:18:46.989 --> 00:19:03.490
Don't let the shiny thing distract you, because there'll be a lot of enticing things in your life that come along to try to deviate you from the plan, just because the anointing is there and people are attracted to the anointing.

00:19:03.490 --> 00:19:12.090
People get attracted to the light, and they'll have all kinds of opportunities, and there'll be money in it and all kinds of things.

00:19:26.220 --> 00:19:26.550
But what does God say?

00:19:26.550 --> 00:19:32.928
No matter how much it looks so pretty and the pig has lipstick, God said, "Don't touch it.

00:19:32.928 --> 00:19:34.747
" He said, "Don't touch it.

00:19:34.747 --> 00:19:44.586
" And there'll be a lot of times He'll instruct you to do things and it doesn't make sense.

00:19:44.586 --> 00:19:46.960
That's what I have for you.

00:19:46.960 --> 00:19:50.800
I pray that blessed you.

00:19:58.720 --> 00:19:58.924
But that's what He's dealing with me on.

00:20:05.680 --> 00:20:08.434
And He said, "From glory to glory, I'm changing you, changing you, changing you into His likeness and image, to perfect in me the love of God shown to the world.

00:20:08.434 --> 00:20:15.218
" For He's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies, His likeness and image, to perfect in me the love of God shown to the world.

00:20:15.218 --> 00:20:16.356
Do you understand?

00:20:17.120 --> 00:20:18.559
He's taking us from glory to glory.

00:20:20.446 --> 00:20:21.177
He's changing me.

00:20:29.840 --> 00:20:30.080
And you've got to keep doing what He's asked you to do, and at all costs.

00:20:34.276 --> 00:20:34.613
And so that's what I have.

00:20:34.613 --> 00:20:39.648
I know this is live, but it's just so raw.

00:20:39.648 --> 00:20:43.919
I'm just so real, y'all, about this kind of stuff.

00:20:43.919 --> 00:20:53.749
I might mess up, and I might say the wrong thing, but I know my heart is trying so hard to tell you what the Holy Spirit has told me today.

00:20:53.749 --> 00:21:00.500
You know, I was outside doing my sprinkler, and it was all messed up.

